ActMinistries and Ministers of State Act
SubjectOrder Terminating the Assignment of the Honourable Rona Ambrose and Assigning the Honourable Rona Ambrose to Assist the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development
PrecisOrder a) Terminating the assignment of the Honourable Rona Ambrose, made by Order in Council P.C. 2010-475 of April 9, 2010, and b) assigning the Honourable RONA AMBROSE as Minister of State to be styled Minister for Status of Women, to assist the Minister of Human Resources and Skills Development, effective May 18, 2011.
